
Ranger Help for: gash
=====================

SYNTAX:      gash <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     75 sp
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:    
Hack allows a Ranger to gash his or her opponent. Its provides a Ranger
with an attack that does good damage. The Ranger must be wielding a
slash type weapon in order to gash.

